{"CLs":[{"__type":"ST","Var":"Info_General"}],"CMT":"To improve commissioning speed, i try to make a big visual feedback on the IAG to see from a long distance the sensor state. But it dosn't work\u000d\u000ain every case: no screen on the machine, in wrong direction, another user change the page, etc.\u000d\u000a\u000d\u000aSo i want to use the buzzer of the line to give an audio feedback of the sensor! On the IAG, you select the sensor you want to hear (all other \u000d\u000asensor will be disabled) and you manipulate the sensor. It will buzz if the sensor is at ON","LRI":1,"RRI":2,"VLs":[]}
